<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        /* üé® MMM95 Meeting Report Styling */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2e7d32 0%, #388e3c 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .meeting-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .info-icon {
            width: 20px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .info-value {
            color: #333;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 30px 0;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #c8e6c9;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .agenda-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .agenda-item {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .agenda-number {
            background: #2e7d32;
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-right: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .agenda-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .agenda-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .agenda-description {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .agenda-meta {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
        }

        .agenda-status {
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .status-completed {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }

        .status-in-progress {
            background: #fff3e0;
            color: #f57c00;
        }

        .status-pending {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            color: #1976d2;
        }

        .participants-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .participant-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .participant-avatar {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #2e7d32;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 auto 10px;
        }

        .participant-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .participant-role {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            background: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .notes-section {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-left: 4px solid #2e7d32;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .note-item {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .note-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .note-author {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }

        .note-date {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .note-content {
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .tasks-section {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .task-item {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .task-checkbox {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            border: 2px solid #2e7d32;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            margin-top: 2px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .task-checkbox.completed {
            background: #2e7d32;
            color: white;
        }

        .task-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .task-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .task-meta {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .summary-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- üìù Meeting Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üìù <%= meeting.baslik %></h1>
        <div class="subtitle"><%= companyName %></div>
        <div style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">
            Rapor Olu≈üturma Tarihi: <%= generatedAt %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- üìã Meeting Information -->
    <div class="meeting-info">
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-icon">üìÖ</span>
                <span class="info-label">Tarih:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= new Date(meeting.tarih).toLocaleDateString('tr-TR') %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-icon">‚è∞</span>
                <span class="info-label">Saat:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= meeting.baslangicSaati %> - <%= meeting.bitisSaati %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-icon">üìç</span>
                <span class="info-label">Lokasyon:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= meeting.lokasyon || 'Online' %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-icon">üë§</span>
                <span class="info-label">Organizat√∂r:</span>
                <span class="info-value"><%= meeting.organizator?.isim || 'Bilinmiyor' %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-icon">üìä</span>
                <span class="info-label">Durum:</span>
                <span class="info-value">
                    <span class="agenda-status <%= meeting.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±' ? 'status-completed' : meeting.durum === 'devam-ediyor' ? 'status-in-progress' : 'status-pending' %>">
                        <%= meeting.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±' ? 'Tamamlandƒ±' : meeting.durum === 'devam-ediyor' ? 'Devam Ediyor' : 'Bekliyor' %>
                    </span>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <span class="info-icon">‚è±Ô∏è</span>
                <span class="info-label">S√ºre:</span>
                <span class="info-value">
                    <% if (meeting.toplamSure) { %>
                        <%= Math.floor(meeting.toplamSure / 60) %>s <%= meeting.toplamSure % 60 %>dk
                    <% } else { %>
                        Hesaplanmadƒ±
                    <% } %>
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- üìä Meeting Statistics -->
    <div class="summary-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number"><%= meeting.katilimcilar?.length || 0 %></div>
            <div class="stat-label">Katƒ±lƒ±mcƒ±</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number"><%= meeting.gundem?.length || 0 %></div>
            <div class="stat-label">G√ºndem Maddesi</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">
                <%= meeting.gundem?.filter(item => item.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±').length || 0 %>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-label">Tamamlanan</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">
                <% if (meeting.gundem?.length > 0) { %>
                    <%= Math.round((meeting.gundem.filter(item => item.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±').length / meeting.gundem.length) * 100) %>%
                <% } else { %>
                    0%
                <% } %>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-label">Tamamlanma</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- üìã Meeting Agenda -->
    <% if (meeting.gundem && meeting.gundem.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">üìã Toplantƒ± G√ºndemi</h2>
            <ul class="agenda-list">
                <% meeting.gundem.forEach((item, index) => { %>
                    <li class="agenda-item">
                        <div class="agenda-number"><%= index + 1 %></div>
                        <div class="agenda-content">
                            <div class="agenda-title"><%= item.baslik %></div>
                            <% if (item.aciklama) { %>
                                <div class="agenda-description"><%= item.aciklama %></div>
                            <% } %>
                            <div class="agenda-meta">
                                <span>‚è±Ô∏è <%= item.sure || 0 %> dakika</span>
                                <% if (item.sorumlu) { %>
                                    <span>üë§ <%= typeof item.sorumlu === 'object' ? item.sorumlu.isim : item.sorumlu %></span>
                                <% } %>
                                <span class="agenda-status <%= item.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±' ? 'status-completed' : item.durum === 'devam-ediyor' ? 'status-in-progress' : 'status-pending' %>">
                                    <%= item.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±' ? 'Tamamlandƒ±' : item.durum === 'devam-ediyor' ? 'Devam Ediyor' : 'Bekliyor' %>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                <% }); %>
            </ul>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- üë• Participants -->
    <% if (meeting.katilimcilar && meeting.katilimcilar.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">üë• Katƒ±lƒ±mcƒ±lar</h2>
            <div class="participants-grid">
                <% meeting.katilimcilar.forEach(participant => { %>
                    <div class="participant-card">
                        <div class="participant-avatar">
                            <%= (participant.kullanici?.isim || participant.isim || 'U')[0].toUpperCase() %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="participant-name">
                            <%= participant.kullanici?.isim || participant.isim || 'Bilinmiyor' %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="participant-role">
                            <%= participant.rol || 'Katƒ±lƒ±mcƒ±' %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- üìù Meeting Notes -->
    <% if (meeting.notlar && meeting.notlar.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">üìù Toplantƒ± Notlarƒ±</h2>
            <div class="notes-section">
                <% meeting.notlar.forEach(note => { %>
                    <div class="note-item">
                        <div class="note-header">
                            <span class="note-author">
                                <%= note.olusturan?.isim || 'Bilinmiyor' %>
                            </span>
                            <span class="note-date">
                                <%= new Date(note.olusturmaTarihi).toLocaleDateString('tr-TR') %>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="note-content"><%= note.icerik %></div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- ‚úÖ Generated Tasks -->
    <% if (meeting.olustrulanGorevler && meeting.olustrulanGorevler.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">‚úÖ Olu≈üturulan G√∂revler</h2>
            <div class="tasks-section">
                <% meeting.olustrulanGorevler.forEach(task => { %>
                    <div class="task-item">
                        <div class="task-checkbox <%= task.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±' ? 'completed' : '' %>">
                            <% if (task.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±') { %>‚úì<% } %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="task-content">
                            <div class="task-title"><%= task.baslik %></div>
                            <div class="task-meta">
                                <span>üë§ <%= task.atanan?.isim || 'Atanmamƒ±≈ü' %></span>
                                <% if (task.bitisTarihi) { %>
                                    <span>üìÖ <%= new Date(task.bitisTarihi).toLocaleDateString('tr-TR') %></span>
                                <% } %>
                                <span>üìä <%= task.oncelik || 'Normal' %></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- üìä Meeting Summary -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">üìä Toplantƒ± √ñzeti</h2>
        <div class="notes-section">
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px;">
                <div>
                    <h4 style="color: #2e7d32; margin-bottom: 10px;">‚úÖ Ba≈üarƒ±lar</h4>
                    <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>Toplantƒ± planlandƒ±ƒüƒ± gibi ger√ßekle≈ütirildi</li>
                        <% if (meeting.gundem?.length > 0) { %>
                            <li><%= meeting.gundem.filter(item => item.durum === 'tamamlandƒ±').length %> g√ºndem maddesi tamamlandƒ±</li>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (meeting.olustrulanGorevler?.length > 0) { %>
                            <li><%= meeting.olustrulanGorevler.length %> adet yeni g√∂rev olu≈üturuldu</li>
                        <% } %>
                        <li>Katƒ±lƒ±mcƒ± etkile≈üimi saƒülandƒ±</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 style="color: #f57c00; margin-bottom: 10px;">‚ö†Ô∏è Dikkat Edilecekler</h4>
                    <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                        <% if (meeting.gundem?.some(item => item.durum !== 'tamamlandƒ±')) { %>
                            <li>Bazƒ± g√ºndem maddeleri tamamlanamadƒ±</li>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (!meeting.toplamSure || meeting.toplamSure > 120) { %>
                            <li>Toplantƒ± s√ºresi optimize edilebilir</li>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (meeting.olustrulanGorevler?.length === 0) { %>
                            <li>Aksiyon planƒ± belirlenmeli</li>
                        <% } %>
                        <li>Takip toplantƒ±sƒ± planlanmalƒ±</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- üìÑ Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Bu rapor MMM95 End√ºstriyel Ekipman Y√∂netim Sistemi tarafƒ±ndan otomatik olarak olu≈üturulmu≈ütur.</p>
        <p>Toplantƒ± ID: <%= meeting._id %> | Rapor tarihi: <%= generatedAt %></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>